like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T16:37:34.000Z","msg":"人一開始點識分善同惡?"},{"pid":"3149326b09cc228e18fc5129ce28b9b01240dfb0","tid":401543,"uid":20241,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T16:37:51.000Z","msg":"本惡<br />\n正如小朋友咩都唔識個時<br />\n有人搶你既零食你會想佢消失行開<br />\n而唔係同佢分享<br />\n呢個就係人既本性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00c02e28f2842860ed13aad9b16c945399a7057c","tid":401543,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T16:41:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本惡<br />\n正如小朋友咩都唔識個時<br />\n有人搶你既零食你會想佢消失行開<br />\n而唔係同佢分享<br />\n呢個就係人既本性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你岩，但你呢種講法太表面<br />\n例如孟子提出人本質有一粒未發芽既善種，人惡只因唔夠善。睇你鐘意邊套"},{"pid":"1f44a1e91b19ed056c81e7c54603869a9c86c5a0","tid":401543,"uid":20241,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T17:23:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>本惡<br />\n正如小朋友咩都唔識個時<br />\n有人搶你既零食你會想佢消失行開<br />\n而唔係同佢分享<br />\n呢個就係人既本性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你岩，但你呢種講法太表面<br />\n例如孟子提出人本質有一粒未發芽既善種，人惡只因唔夠善。睇你鐘意邊套</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢太離地啦<br />\n當然資源數之不盡時 人人都無慾無求時個個都善<br />\n<br />\n但呢個世界上資源永遠都滿足唔曬所有人<br />\n人永遠都有慾望<br />\n慾望就係惡既根源"},{"pid":"bbd95bc7042aa686a452dd4837efe3a56be963f9","tid":401543,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T17:41:04.000Z","msg":"本惡"},{"pid":"ce996f4974bddfa9053fd95c1eda1950fdecc4e3","tid":401543,"uid":44916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T17:41:22.000Z","msg":"混合"},{"pid":"ce38a598f9ff63355b34bec5bff485aff92449cd","tid":401543,"uid":128869,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T04:44:49.000Z","msg":"依孟子同荀子講 人係善惡為根<br />\n惡者，為人之動物性。即所有動物通用，例如佔有、食慾、性慾......<br />\n善者，為人之獨特性/道德性。如果人覺悟啟發其善，則該人之善可凌駕於惡，例如為了道德而不食不道德之食物，甚或因此餓死。"},{"pid":"f124e079a1a27bbaf99570be13a11126bf9d3fbf","tid":401543,"uid":2615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T04:46:11.000Z","msg":"每個人都唔同"},{"pid":"d60a56b100bf13f0b93a776f9fc0f2f331c32bdb","tid":401543,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T07:12:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依孟子同荀子講 人係善惡為根<br />\n惡者，為人之動物性。即所有動物通用，例如佔有、食慾、性慾......<br />\n善者，為人之獨特性/道德性。如果人覺悟啟發其善，則該人之善可凌駕於惡，例如為了道德而不食不道德之食物，甚或因此餓死。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n知道會死人肉你都食架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b60730708ca003936615cb7613bb3fd7e0bb59cd","tid":401543,"uid":59179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T07:14:03.000Z","msg":"都有"},{"pid":"d1282cab5ab4c7e354aec90c8ea5d0d46e9db38e","tid":401543,"uid":17335,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T07:26:09.000Z","msg":"可供參考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人性本惡？站於時代回應之真相&mdash;&mdash;荀子性惡篇（一）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://deliver90.blogspot.tw/2017/03/blog-post_6.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdeliver90.blogspot.tw%2F2017%2F03%2Fblog-post_6.html%3Fm%3D1&d=6bRBsjvaQvTFxjMKpneUsZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=b070d915\" target=\"_blank\">http://deliver90.blogspot.tw/2017/03/blog-post_6.html?m=1</a><br />\n<br />\n簡介基本古代思想概念：性 兼讀韓非子外儲說左上篇、六反篇之控制人性的趨利避害<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://deliver90.blogspot.tw/2017/07/ep11.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdeliver90.blogspot.tw%2F2017%2F07%2Fep11.html%3Fm%3D1&d=6bRBsjvaQvTFxjMKpneUsZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=75e01625\" target=\"_blank\">http://deliver90.blogspot.tw/2017/07/ep11.html?m=1</a>"},{"pid":"6e98d44a13db0d6989274f289eb438ed7b5567dd","tid":401543,"uid":128869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T08:37:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可供參考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人性本惡？站於時代回應之真相&mdash;&mdash